-- Berkshire Buys Greensboro News & Record as Buffett Bets on Media
-- B y   E l i z a b e t h   B u n n
-- 2013-01-31T17:44:46Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-01-31/berkshire-buys-greensboro-news-record-as-buffett-bets-on-media.html
Warren Buffett ’s Berkshire Hathaway
Inc. bought the Greensboro News & Record from Landmark Media
Enterprises as the billionaire investor’s firm extends a bet on
community newspapers.  The newspaper has daily circulation of 58,000, and 86,000
on Sunday, the media unit at Omaha, Nebraska-based Berkshire
said today in an e-mailed statement that didn’t disclose terms.  To contact the reporter on this story:
